text:
@benbatemanmedia Ugh.
From the overnight, head-slapping simplicity of acquiring time travel (distinct from the method already shown to exist) to the many characters recklessly/needlessly removing masks/helmets in a war zone...
this movie was problematic all over the place.
It let me down a lot.

2020 has shown us how fickle life is, so next year do not hold back! Book that flight. Get that tattoo. Apply for that opportunity. Say â€œI love youâ€ more. Watch that movie. Stop procrastinating. Block that person. Start that business. Take that risk. Live while you can!
